'''Kintaq''', or '''Kentaq Bong''', is an [[Austroasiatic languages|Austroasiatic]] language spoken in [[Malaysia]] and [[Thailand]]. It belongs to the [[Northern Aslian]] sub-branch of the [[Aslian languages|Aslian]] languages. The small number of speakers is decreasing.
